statements: SELECT user_id, start_time, end_time, duration_minutes, distance_km FROM BikeSharingUsage WHERE user_id = 1234;

SELECT r.rental_id, u.username, s.station_name, rl.log_date FROM bike_rentals r INNER JOIN bike_users u ON r.user_id = u.user_id INNER JOIN bike_stations s ON r.station_id = s.station_id INNER JOIN bike_logs rl ON r.rental_id = rl.rental_id WHERE u.city = 'Los Angeles' AND r.return_date IS NULL ORDER BY rl.log_date ASC;
SELECT u.username, COUNT(distinct r.rental_id) AS total_rentals FROM bike_users u LEFT JOIN bike_rentals r ON u.user_id = r.user_id GROUP BY u.username HAVING total_rentals > 3;

SELECT r.rental_date, SUM(l.distance_km) AS total_distance FROM bike_rentals r INNER JOIN bike_logs l ON r.rental_id = l.rental_id WHERE r.rental_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31' GROUP BY r.rental_date ORDER BY total_distance DESC;
